{"tid":2427992,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始：一名市民注射科興疫苗後心悸正留醫　情況穩定","createTime":"2021-03-01T08:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T09:30:30.000Z","uid":241764,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b4fd3489c75da729bc33b51a37f04d763bb55162","tid":2427992,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T08:25:48.000Z","msg":"她重申現時兩款到港的科興及復必泰疫苗，都經過專家審核，接種效益高於風險，呼籲市民支持接種計劃。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始說，衞生署將加強恆常監測機制，設立網上呈報系統，讓醫護人員呈報異常事件，再進行因果關係評估，確認事件與疫苗接種有關，署方亦已編定兩款疫苗的接種須知，詳細列出預期出現的副作用。<br />\n<br />\n至於有市民接種疫苗後出現心悸情況，她表示，將交由衞生署評估，再研究是否獲疫苗保障基金賠償。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578120-20210301.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578120-20210301.htm&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3acrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=c4a89416\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578120-20210301.htm&h=86ffea72\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578120-20210301.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n一定係收咗美國佬錢扮心悸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1e43a2ecd002b260c3b6f29e424ecaa68a1205","tid":2427992,"uid":276273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:08:45.000Z","msg":"無錢賠，就算死咗，都要用儀器谷d維生指數出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab5ee48b177e55f3e3b85613e755b714e5d8376","tid":2427992,"uid":320902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:26:02.000Z","msg":"信正苦，唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749da7ccc22b925f1eafaac312cbc76b2c17790a","tid":2427992,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:28:49.000Z","msg":"唔評論個別事件"},{"pid":"03a13fb0bee7c8a44847962d18b8165b94dbdad4","tid":2427992,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike"